{"id":106529,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/谁动了邓小平、胡锦涛的合照（图）/","date":"2010-09-22T02:24:24Z","modified":"2010-09-22T18:27:42Z","title":"谁动了邓小平、胡锦涛的合照（图）","content":"<p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/12333/2\">www.flickr.com &#8211; FeedzShare</a></p>\n<p>发布时间:2010年09月20日,  已有 6 人推荐</p>\n<hr />\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/92/253243888_3c46221386.jpg\" alt=\"張相片\" width=\"500\" height=\"451\" /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h1>谁动了邓小平胡锦涛的合照</h1>\n<div>\n<p>邓小平众里寻他，在人群中找到胡锦涛，两人亲切握手，是一帧极其珍贵的照片。</p>\n<p>这一帧由邓小平亲自肯定胡锦涛身份的照片，拍摄于1992年10月，具体在哪一天则仍然是个谜。</p>\n<p>更大的谜是这一帧丝毫不会有损中共利益的照片，为何要等到今年纪念邓小平百岁冥寿时才得以向公众披露？</p>\n<p>最大的谜团是，同一帧照片，竟有三个版本，亚洲时报在线为此制作了一个比较图。</p>\n<p>综合比对了三帧照片后，可以肯定指出，原载于今年8月19日出版《了望东方》周刊的(最大图)，光线自然真实，是唯一真正照片。</p>\n<p>照片中，邓小平在小女儿邓榕搀扶下与胡锦涛亲切握手，胡的后面前排站著中共13届部份政治局委员，包括吴邦国、秦基伟、李锡铭、李铁映等，后排站的显然是出席中共14大的较高级代表。邓胡两人后侧站著江泽民、杨尚昆、乔石、万里等中共13届政治局常委级领导。</p>\n<p>这一帧照片，足以衬托出邓小平隔代交班予胡锦涛的气势，江泽民在照片中只是一个主要陪客而已。</p>\n<p>然而，有机会看到这照片的人，在全中国可能不够一个百分点或千分点。</p>\n<p>绝大多数中国人通过各大媒体看到的，是新华社在两个多星期前发布的一帧照片（有Xinhua字的小图）。照片后面没有了江泽民，连其他政治局委员都失迹了，被抹掉了。取而代之是黑压压的一大堆出席会议代表。</p>\n<p>细心阅读，不难看出是一帧做了手脚的照片，主角人物和背景之间的光线完全不对称。</p>\n<p>最令人拍案叫绝的，是胡锦涛自己珍藏的照片，后面就漆黑一片，连做手脚找来的普通代表们作为布景也省了。而这帧假照片竟堂而皇之挂在邓小平百年诞辰展览中（有文汇报字的小图）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3>回應和最愛</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<div><a name=\"comment72157594304214609\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/gigijin/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/23/buddyicons/60853967@N00.jpg?1218662873#60853967@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a name=\"comment72157594304214609\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/gigijin/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/23/buddyicons/60853967@N00.jpg?1218662873#60853967@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<p><span><br />\n<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/gigijin/\">gigijin</a> </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<small><br />\n(<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/rainbowsoft/253243888/comment72157594304214609/\">48個月前</a></span><span> </span>)<br />\n</small></p>\n<div>\n<p>有意思&#8230;</p>\n<p>政治这东西&#8230;哎</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><span>★</span></div>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/jzhang/favorites/with/253243888/\">jzhang533</a>, <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/comer/favorites/with/253243888/\">ComerZhao</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/niechen/favorites/with/253243888/\">乜晨</a> added this photo to their favorites.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><a name=\"comment72157594304445951\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/niechen/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/48/buddyicons/90201780@N00.jpg?1250242185#90201780@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a name=\"comment72157594304445951\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/niechen/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/48/buddyicons/90201780@N00.jpg?1250242185#90201780@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<p><span><br />\n<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/niechen/\">乜晨</a> </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<small><br />\n(<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/rainbowsoft/253243888/comment72157594304445951/\">48個月前</a></span><span> </span>)<br />\n</small></p>\n<div>\n<p>还真没注意</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><span>★</span></div>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/snowyowls/favorites/with/253243888/\">snowyowls_ added this photo to their favorites.</a><br />\n<small>(48個月前)</small></p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><a name=\"comment72157594311191995\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/kami_sama/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/142/buddyicons/91744608@N00.jpg?1213232591#91744608@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a name=\"comment72157594311191995\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/kami_sama/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/142/buddyicons/91744608@N00.jpg?1213232591#91744608@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<p><span><br />\n<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/kami_sama/\">Euphrates Achates</a> <a title=\"升級為 Pro 的方式\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/upgrade/\"></a></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<small><br />\n(<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/rainbowsoft/253243888/comment72157594311191995/\">48個月前</a></span><span> </span>)<br />\n</small></p>\n<div>\n<p>呵呵</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><span>★</span></div>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/dancemoon/favorites/with/253243888/\">dancemoon added this photo to his favorites.</a><br />\n<small>(48個月前)</small></p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><a name=\"comment72157600230194787\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/faydao/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/55/buddyicons/62405186@N00.jpg?1148725417#62405186@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a name=\"comment72157600230194787\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/faydao/\"><img src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/55/buddyicons/62405186@N00.jpg?1148725417#62405186@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<p><span><br />\n<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/faydao/\">小刀周远</a> </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<small><br />\n(<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/rainbowsoft/253243888/comment72157600230194787/\">41個月前</a></span><span> </span>)<br />\n</small></p>\n<div>\n<p>果真NB。</p>\n<p>党国多是PS高手～</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><a name=\"comment72157606641667094\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/mosesofmason/\"><img src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2082/buddyicons/13702257@N00.jpg?1200274557#13702257@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a name=\"comment72157606641667094\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/mosesofmason/\"><img src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2082/buddyicons/13702257@N00.jpg?1200274557#13702257@N00\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<p><span><br />\n<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/mosesofmason/\">mosesofmason</a> </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<small><br />\n(<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/rainbowsoft/253243888/comment72157606641667094/\">26個月前</a></span><span> </span>)<br />\n</small></p>\n<div>\n<p>中共篡改历史照片是有传统的了, 当年多少照片被篡改, 甚至还被选入教科书.<br />\n那些被篡改的人就像从来没在历史上存在过一样, 从历史中消失了. 对比起来,<br />\n这张图里的篡改真是一点都不为奇.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><span>★</span></div>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/onflickr/favorites/with/253243888/\">@blackdream</a>, <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/jonathan-gonse/favorites/with/253243888/\">jonathangonse</a>, <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/hauy/favorites/with/253243888/\">hauy</a>, <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/faydao/favorites/with/253243888/\">小刀周远</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/rainbowsoft/253243888/favorites/\">2 other people</a> added this photo to their favorites.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><a name=\"comment72157624869647069\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/bustop23/\"><img src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3469/buddyicons/41357984@N04.jpg?1249955406#41357984@N04\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a name=\"comment72157624869647069\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/bustop23/\"><img src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3469/buddyicons/41357984@N04.jpg?1249955406#41357984@N04\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<p><span><br />\n<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/bustop23/\">Hu Kun</a> </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<small><br />\n(<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/rainbowsoft/253243888/comment72157624869647069/\">5小時前</a></span><span> </span>)<br />\n</small></p>\n<div>\n<p>不过照片的篡改只是一小部分，而被篡改的文字和历史又有谁能说清，谁能看清呢？</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div><span>★</span></div>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/lwl/favorites/with/253243888/\">Wenliang</a>, <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/46220188@N04/favorites/with/253243888/\">orezna</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.